3000 members! Where does that put us?¶

In [3]:
%matplotlib inline
import numpy as np
import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
sns.set_style("whitegrid")

f, ax = plt.subplots(1, 1, figsize=(8, 6))

data = {
    'London.ai': 364,
    'London Data Science': 1125,
    'Data Science Lab': 1713,
    'Data Natives London': 1837,
    'TLPG': 2203,
    'Big Data Developrs in London': 2630,
    'London Machine Learning Meetup': 2969,
    'PyData London': 3075, 
    'Big Data London': 4344,
    'Data Science London': 6241, 
}

for tick in ax.get_xticklabels():
    tick.set_rotation(90)

df = pd.DataFrame({'Members': list(data.values())}, index=data.keys())
df = df.sort_values('Members').transpose()

sns.barplot(data=df)
ax.set_ylabel('Members')
ax.set_xlabel('Groups')
